Step 9 — Copy Security files from Admin Service
Copy these files exactly — just change package name to com.parking.booking.*:

JwtUtil.java → com.parking.booking.security
JwtAuthFilter.java → com.parking.booking.filter
SecurityConfig.java → com.parking.booking.config
Exception classes → com.parking.booking.exception
GlobalExceptionHandler.java → com.parking.booking.exception

For SecurityConfig.java change the authorized paths:
java.authorizeHttpRequests(auth -> auth
    .requestMatchers("/actuator/**").permitAll()
    .requestMatchers("/api/bookings/**").authenticated()
    .anyRequest().authenticated()
)
